libeddsa
------------------------------------------
This is a small cryptographic library for signatures with ed25519 and
diffie-hellman key exchange with x25519.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libeddsa-devel-0.8+git20231114-1bl1
  libeddsa0-0.8+git20231114-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/phlay/libeddsa

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/phlay/libeddsa.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libeddsa-0.8+git20231114-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libeddsa-0.8+git20231114-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libeddsa-0.8+git20231114-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libeddsa-0.8+git20231114-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libeddsa0-0.8+git20231114-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libeddsa-devel-0.8+git20231114-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libeddsa)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libeddsa.README
  /usr/share/doc/libeddsa/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libeddsa/README.md

(libeddsa0)
  /usr/bin/cygeddsa-0.dll

(libeddsa-devel)
  /usr/include/eddsa.h
  /usr/lib/libeddsa.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libeddsa.pc

